CSS units Absolute
--------------------
1. cm - centimeters
2. mm - millimeters
3. in - inches
4. px - Pixels(1px = 1/96th of 1in)
5 pt - Points(1pt = 1/72 of 1in)
6. pc Picas(1pc = 12pt)

CSS units = relative
--------------------
1. % - to parent element
2. em - To font-size of parent element (ex: 1.2em is 1.2 times of fontsize of parent element)
3. rem - to font-size of root element
4. vw - to 1% of viewport width
5. vh - to 1% of viewport height